      "instruction": "<p>Top your <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with a dollop of <strong>mango mayo</strong>, the <strong>spiced chicken</strong>, a handful of <strong>curried slaw </strong>and the <strong>toasted brioche lid </strong>– this is your <strong>Indian-style chicken burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>paprika fries</strong> and <strong>remaining curried slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
